          "_name": "content2",
          "_customHTML": "<section class=\"content2 mbr-section article\" plugins=\"amp-main\">\n    \n    <mbr-parameters>\n    <!-- Block parameters controls (Blue \"Gear\" panel) -->\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"3\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"1\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Background Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    <!-- End block parameters -->\n    </mbr-parameters> \n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"mbr-row mbr-justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"mbr-col-sm-12 mbr-col-md-10 mbr-col-lg-8\">\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-fonts-style mbr-section-title mbr-light\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\">（三）政策措施类</h3>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-article>我们将政策措施类共97条谣言分为五大类，分别为：出行、开学、消毒、停业、其他。出行(39条)：与人员出行流动有关的谣言，如封城、道路管制等；医疗(15条)：与医院、医疗用品等有关的谣言，如口罩的购买发放途径等；开学(14条)：与各级学校复课有关的谣言；消毒(11条)：各省市区内使用不同途径抗疫消毒；停业(8条)：受到疫情影响，企事业单位停止工作；其它(11条)：其它难以归类的。<br></p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
